  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Consolidation of community based early warning system in India and Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is expected to improve the capacity of district line department on  multi hazard risk mitigation activities. Strengthening of CBOs, CSOs and PRIs on updated technology on CBEWS so that many lives can be saved during the disasters. The impact study to be published will enhance the promotion of CBEWS and will support in scaling up.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is to adapt replication model of CBEWS in Devipatan division of Bihar through advocacy with administration, local institution and corporate sector. Strengthening the capacities of CSOs, CBOs and local administration on various techniques of river monitoring systems and information dissemination etc. To conduct study and impact evaluation of trans border early warning system in consultation with various stakeholders. school safety audit of selected schools along with demonstration of best practices to be conducted on EWS. To publish the study on multi hazard risk reduction plan for district Bahraich.</narrative>
  </description>
